商业并重的阶段。 500 亿元的融资目标，若成功完成，将使其成为中国人工智能公司历史上规模最大的单轮融资。这不仅凸显了资本市场对 DeepSeek 技术实力的高度认可，也反映出在 AI 赛道竞争日趋白热化的背景下，头部玩家对资金储备的迫切需求。 目前，DeepSeek 、腾讯方面暂未对此消息置评。DeepSeek 被曝融资 500 亿，梁文锋占大头，估值直冲 3500 亿 感谢 IT 之家网友补药吖的线索投递！ IT 之家 5 月 6 日消息，据《金融时报》刚刚报道，国家集成电路产业投资基金（简称「国家大基金」）正在与 DeepSeek 洽谈主导其首轮融资事宜，其最终估值有望定在 450 亿美元（IT 之家注：现汇率约合 3077.95 亿元人民币）左右。估值近 450 亿美元，deepseek 首轮融资获「国家大基金」领投磋商"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-c31a0f3760ab3d534b00d61f2b17d8ce_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "87 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2035400318624733173"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIxrr3mInwvYIcEAMaCTExOTQwMzk3OCCjgOzPBjAAOIkFQBFyEzIwMzU0MDAzMTg2MjQ3MzMxNzN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "18_1778419160.413556", "card_id": "Q_2035295747474763944", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 31}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待新一代 SU7 上市 48 天，锁单超过 80000 台？只公布锁单数据是否会被其他车企跟进？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "5 月 6 日，小米汽车官宣，新一代 SU7 上市 48 天，锁单已超过 80000 台。小米创始人雷军也在个人微博发文，感谢车主朋友们的认可。小米新一代 SU7 锁单超 80000 台"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "86 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2035295747474763944"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIxrr3mInwvYIcEAMaCTExOTM5ODMzNCDAverPBjAAOCFAEnITMjAzNTI5NTc0NzQ3NDc2Mzk0NHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1778419160.414146", "card_id": "Q_2035416214772642833", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 16}, "target":